<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forget Password Activation Link</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2>Dear {{name}},</h2>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password. To proceed, please click the button below:</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
            <a href="{{activationLink}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Reset Password</a>
        </div>
        <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>support@casualPro.me</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
